Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.00,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Life It goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.66,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}爛れた世界だって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.74,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}嘆いてるその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.57,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}神風よ誘え
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.76,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}未知なる方ヘ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:53.06,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}沸き上がる情熱と
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.56,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燻る魂が胸を締め付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.92,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃える緋の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.28,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}There I'll find my place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.81,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Under the rader I'm reaching for the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:15.31,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鋼の牙を起て
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:23.84,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}呻きと声を挙げ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:31.07,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}I'm gonna live out my life untamed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:17.62,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}たった―つのこの身焦がして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:22.57,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}血が枯れはてるまで進む
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:32.23,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}遠い空から反る光もこの身に当たり消え
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.09,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}散ってゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:42.13,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}荒ぶる波動を内に抱えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:56.56,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}握り締めた手の疼きは誰も知るはずなく！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.31,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊せ Break & Peace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.91,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}音も無く迫る闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:08.32,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.58,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.13,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:20.44,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.26,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:17.42,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:22.22,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:26.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:30.62,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.00,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.66,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:41.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:45.57,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:47.76,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:53.06,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.21,0:02:58.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:02.92,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:05.28,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:08.81,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:15.31,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:23.84,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:31.07,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:17.62,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:22.57,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:32.23,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}远方天空反射过来的光照耀此身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.09,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}消逝散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:42.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸中充满激烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:56.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}紧握的手的疼痛谁人能知!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.31,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.91,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悄无声息迫近的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:08.32,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}只为点亮光明  现在正是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.58,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}用与生俱来的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:20.44,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}抓住一切 就是现在 只要……
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.26,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}将真实握在手中！
